<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Metkor yr headline shr slips, div up.</title>
<headline>Metkor yr headline shr slips, div up.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended March 31</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>Shr, (cts)</p>
<p>    - headline		    25.0    vs    49.0</p>
<p>    - attrib			38.4    vs    53.0</p>
<p>    Div (cts)		     14.8    vs    12.9</p>
<p>    Attrib income		46.32    vs    63.87</p>
<p>    Pre-tax		     192.28    vs    228.94</p>
<p>    Tax			    52.05    vs    73.45</p>
<p>    Interest recieved	   5.89    vs    7.11</p>
<p>    Turnover		  3,534.89    vs    3,413.87</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	  36.94    vs    6.91</p>
<p>    Share of associates'     21.41    vs    11.12</p>
<p>Div payable July 4</p>
<p>on register June 13</p>
<p>Full name: Metkor Group Ltd (engineering)</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said the restructuring of Dorbyl Ltd was virtually complete and the group was poised to achive steady growth.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
